            END.
        END.
    
        RUN som.p(INPUT "music\ok.wav").

        {&OPEN-QUERY-{&BROWSE-NAME}}
        REPOSITION br-page1 TO ROWID rTemp.
    
        RUN recalcula IN THIS-PROCEDURE.
    
